data.description: Elevate your lifestyle with this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom sanctuary nestled just a stone's throw from the majestic Intracoastal Waterway. Prepare to be spellbound by the endless panoramic views and the freedom of owning a home without the confines of an HOA or subdivision rules.  Why This Home is Your Next Haven:  Intracoastal Bliss: Indulge in the luxury of waking up to breathtaking water vistas, inviting you to savor every sunrise and sunset from your own slice of paradise. Freedom Unleashed: Say goodbye to limitations. This is a home where your imagination reigns supreme – no HOA, no subdivision restrictions. It's your canvas to create the lifestyle you've always envisioned. Serene Seclusion: Tucked away in a tranquil enclave, this haven offers the peace and serenity you crave, a retreat from the hustle and bustle while being just moments away from coastal adventures.  This isn't just a home; it's a gateway to an extraordinary lifestyle. Imagine waking up to the tranquil sounds of the water, relishing the freedom to customize your surroundings, and basking in the unparalleled beauty of the Intracoastal at your doorstep.  This rare gem won't linger on the market for long. Act now to secure your ticket to coastal bliss – a home that promises not just a place to live, but a canvas to craft your dream lifestyle.
